      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly got to see this absolute gem in person. I have pampered this car since day one, and it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives like an absolute dream\u2014so smooth and responsive. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the new car price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it just as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
