      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies to a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. This example boasts proactive mechanical stewardship: the VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid with no bushing deflection, while the exterior retains its original deep luster. A turn-key, investment-quality icon for the discerning purist.",
